INSTALL WITH SETUP.RB

How to install:
  ruby setup.rb config
  ruby setup.rb setup
  ruby setup.rb install

The quick way (as root):
  ruby setup.rb   

For more options issue:
  ruby setup.rb help

For more info on usage of the setup.rb script have a look at:
  http://i.loveruby.net/en/projects/setup/doc/usage.html


INSTALL WITHOUT SETUP.RB

Copy the bin/rsdownloader.rb script to some suitable place preferably 
in your $PATH



  
